			<span class="posted-on"><a href="/cvety-i-rasteniya/aloe-variegata.html" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2019-11-30T11:02:24+03:00">30.11.2019</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="/author/lecya">lecya</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
